CREATED:20260302T202656Z
DESCRIPTION:Bear Grease is an unapologetically Indigenous musical and a lo
 ving clap back to the classic hit Grease-reimagined through the lens of I
 ndigenous culture\, language\, song\, and humor. Created by husband-and-w
 ife duo LightningCloud and born on Treaty 6 territory in Alberta\, this g
 rassroots sensation has become a North American touring phenomenon\, perf
 orming over 200 shows in community centers\, powwow grounds\, and major t
 heaters alike. With powwow beats\, high-energy choreography\, laugh-out-l
 oud storytelling\, and an all-Indigenous cast\, Bear Grease is equal part
 s comedy\, cultural reclamation\, and theatrical celebration. This produc
 tion radiates a sense of pride and joy that audiences carry with them lon
 g after the final bow.
DURATION:PT2H
DTSTAMP:20260302T202656Z
