CREATED:20260403T145011Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Duke Arts at the Fruit in downtown Durham for an evening 
 showcase of student creative work from Duke Arts Studio. Eight Duke stude
 nts paired with professional artists and Duke alums spent the 2025-2026 a
 cademic year writing\, filming\, sculpting\, styling and creating origina
 l works. Each student artist will present a selection of their work in an
  exciting mix of live demonstrations\, readings\, screenings\, and visual
  art exhibitions. Learn more about the unique and powerful projects in ou
 r cohort announcement. Stick around after the presentation for a receptio
 n with heavy hors d'oeuvres and desserts.
DURATION:PT2H
