CONTACT;X-BEDEWORK-UID=00f1fcdb-0f068baf-010f-068baf83-00000004:None
CREATED:20260331T172045Z
DESCRIPTION:Film Screening and Q&A for Edhi Alice: Reverse\n\n\nKeeping th
 e camera close\, the film follows two transitioning women\, Edhi and Alic
 e\, as they seek to reconcile their bodies and identities. Through divers
 e cinematic forms\, their experiences unfold into a larger question: what
  defines a trans woman and what\, in turn\, defines cinema itself?\n\n\nF
 ollowing the screening of the documentary film\, there will be a Q&A sess
 ion led by Professor Sung Eun Kim from AMES\, featuring the director\, pr
 oducers\, and cast members.\n\n\nThis event is sponsored by AMES\, APSI\,
  Duke Arts\, CSGD\, Theater Studies\, CDS\, GSFS\, AAHVS
DTSTAMP:20260401T181704Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260416T193000
